metadata.name: Inner light
metadata.description:
When there is darkness around you, only your inner light gives you strength.  
This work is about me, about my feelings this winter and spring, when the war began. It was the darkest time in my life, only faith in goodness gives strength to live. I'm a dreamer. This is my message to me and to the people around me, that even in these current times, there is a light and a dream within us, and they illuminate our path.
